{"tid":2040573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃圈龍頭 龍門","createTime":"2020-05-28T16:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T06:50:08.000Z","uid":186851,"like":7,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dee4c00c2fd8ad22711ea1d38ea7e233a03e4e88","tid":2040573,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"龍門自認黃店先鋒<br />\n但就連一場罷工都未參與過<br />\n<br />\n饅頭張點解可以咁無恥，話自己係打頭陣嘅黃店？！黃店呢個概念係7/8月就有，但龍門係8月中同富臨割蓆先首次開聲，9月先忽然變黃，饅頭張 11月嗰陣連選民都唔係！<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/822435581595690/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F401516367020949%2Fpermalink%2F822435581595690%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=1117679f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/401516367020949/permalink/822435581595690/</a><br />\n<br />\n7月8月龍門响度做緊乜？咪Po餐牌囉！721冇譴責白衣人，831 冇譴責黑警，大家睇吓龍門721同831啲post，係直頭唔知有事發生過咁呀！咁仲扮乜撚嘢黃圈先鋒呀饅頭張？！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgV60De.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgV60De.jpg&h=b69dc273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那來勇氣話自己打頭陣 🤣🤣🤣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁六月蘋果純計果班打頭陣罷工612果d黃店叫乜？ 😌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59697013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59697013&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuzk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=197f51ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59697013&h=e2ccf0b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190612/59697013</a><br />\n<br />\n👆👆 龍門呢？ 死左去邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b223c43a8393a4bc026e7c3e17e3c73c3931e7","tid":2040573,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit